metadata.description:
We are Medusa World DAO, a community powered by an NFT with 6 utilities.

Dedicated to build, and find concrete solutions to regenerate the planet, IRL. 40% of our income go to active NGOs that have a positive impact on our ecosystems. See our pre-mint IRL actions on our social media.

6 utilities:

1: NGO fund: 40% donated to a number of NGOs, and carbon credit production

2: Eco-book to save energy, carbon emissions and money on a daily basis

3: Rewards Program: airdrops, IRL experiences, sustainable trips, eco-friendly prizes, etc

4: Shared Royalties: 40% to NGOs, 30% to Members, 30% to Treasury

5: Genius Cup: 5% to support innovative and sustainable projects

6: Art with a message to be pushed on social media to incentivise people to take action
